    .grid.grid-cols-1.md:grid-cols-2.gap-8
      .bg-white.dark:bg-gray-800.p-6.rounded-lg.shadow-lg{data: {aos: "fade-up", aos_duration: "1000"}}
        %h3.text-xl.font-bold.mb-4.text-gray-900.dark:text-gray-100 What is spirulina?
        %p.text-lg.text-gray-600.dark:text-gray-300 Spirulina is a type of blue-green algae that grows in both fresh and salt water. It is known for its high protein and vitamin content and is often used as a dietary supplement.
      .bg-white.dark:bg-gray-800.p-6.rounded-lg.shadow-lg{data: {aos: "fade-up", aos_duration: "1500"}}
        %h3.text-xl.font-bold.mb-4.text-gray-900.dark:text-gray-100 How should I consume spirulina?
        %p.text-lg.text-gray-600.dark:text-gray-300 Spirulina can be consumed in various forms, including powder, tablets, and capsules. It can be mixed into smoothies, juices, or water, or taken as a supplement.
      .bg-white.dark:bg-gray-800.p-6.rounded-lg.shadow-lg{data: {aos: "fade-up", aos_duration: "2000"}}
        %h3.text-xl.font-bold.mb-4.text-gray-900.dark:text-gray-100 Are there any side effects of spirulina?
        %p.text-lg.text-gray-600.dark:text-gray-300 Spirulina is generally safe for most people, but some may experience mild side effects such as nausea or an upset stomach. It is recommended to start with a small dose and gradually increase it.
      .bg-white.dark:bg-gray-800.p-6.rounded-lg.shadow-lg{data: {aos: "fade-up", aos_duration: "2500"}}
        %h3.text-xl.font-bold.mb-4.text-gray-900.dark:text-gray-100 Where can I buy Machinery co. products?
        %p.text-lg.text-gray-600.dark:text-gray-300 Machinery co. products can be purchased through our official website, as well as through various online and offline retailers.

